{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2794709, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 532433, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "非加速器专业，回答可能不对。但感觉不可能，要想达到这么大的能量，装置不可能这么小。", "timestamp": 1635178589, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2794798, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 532433, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "激光切割没啥问题，但是合成新元素需要核反应了，可能需要比较高的能量", "timestamp": 1635178913, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2794822, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 532433, "reply_to": 2794709, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 那在电影的设定中，托尼家里是有核反应堆的(这好像也是工物的范畴)，以核反应堆提供能量的话是不是有实现的可能呢？", "timestamp": 1635178997, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2794894, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 675, "w": 1200}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 532433, "reply_to": 2794798, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: ", "timestamp": 1635179225, "type": "image", "url": "n3/n3t7e7z522ojde7mdefbfpk24fhe36ta.jpeg"}, {"cid": 2794906, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 532433, "reply_to": 2794822, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 不是能量这么简单，主要还是受到材料限制。要加速粒子需要超强的电磁场，只要产生电场或磁场的设备不能小型化，就不可能。", "timestamp": 1635179272, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2794912, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 532433, "reply_to": 2794822, "tag": null, "text": "比如关键在于超导材料，如果常温超导能实现，那么现在实现可控核聚变发电也不是问题了。所以希望材料系的同学给点力吧😂", "timestamp": 1635179341, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2794919, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 532433, "reply_to": 2794798, "tag": null, "text": "大爱托尼，他在工程物理、机械工程、电子工程等方向都是顶尖水平，可惜只是虚构出来的人物", "timestamp": 1635179381, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2794942, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 532433, "reply_to": 2794912, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 唉，现在“生化环材”并称四大天坑，人人避之不及，真不知道这些高尖端技术什么时候能突破", "timestamp": 1635179533, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2795006, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 532433, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "科幻迷也不应该迷漫威啊。。", "timestamp": 1635179848, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2795017, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 532433, "reply_to": 2795006, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 武侠玄幻迷", "timestamp": 1635179912, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2795555, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 532433, "reply_to": 2795006, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 银河护卫队、奇异博士再到无限宝石确实是扯了，但把钢铁侠单独拎出来看还是属于科幻的，对吧", "timestamp": 1635182440, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2795710, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 532433, "reply_to": 2795555, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 大分类勉强算广义科幻，其实是奇幻", "timestamp": 1635183664, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2796314, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 532433, "reply_to": 2795710, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 找六块无限宝石是奇幻、玄幻，但钢铁侠外骨骼、加速器、冷核聚变就是科幻", "timestamp": 1635205241, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2796480, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 532433, "reply_to": 2796314, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 软科幻软也要有限度的", "timestamp": 1635210134, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2797890, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 532433, "reply_to": 2796480, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 对喽，钢铁侠就在限度之内", "timestamp": 1635225348, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2805474, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 532433, "reply_to": 2797890, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 你算算他那个加速度能活不🐶", "timestamp": 1635327377, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 400, "w": 600}, "likenum": 6, "pid": 532433, "reply": 16, "tag": null, "text": "想真心请教工物系的同学一个问题，本人是一名科幻迷，喜欢钢铁侠，想问一下《钢铁侠2》中托尼在家里自己造了一个加速器来合成新元素，并且加速出来的光线能够切断书架、金属，这在现实生活中是否可能实现呢？", "timestamp": 1635178251, "type": "image", "updated_at": 1635327379, "url": "nr/nre36vpql6l6d72undivynysfgqgmckj.jpeg", "vote": {}}}